Package: familia
Title: R Shiny Application for Ancestry Assessments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
              person("Josue", "Chinchilla-Vargas",
                    role = c("aut","cre"),
                    email = "josue.chinchilla@ufl.edu"),
              person(c("Alexander", "M."), "Sandercock",
                    role = "aut"),
              person("Breeding Insight Team",
                    role = "aut"))
Description: This R shiny app provides a web-based user friendly way for researchers to analyze genomic data without needing to use command-line tools.
             Ancestry methods such as snmf() and PolyBreedTools are provided for researchers to evaluate the ancestry of plant and animal samples through
             supervised and unsupervised approaches.
